high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn left and walk up to the tub.
Pick up the leftmost black rag out of the tub.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn left and walk up to the sink.
Put the black rag on the small white dresser that is to the right of the sink.
Turn left and walk up to the tub.
Pick up the black rag out of the tub.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left to face the small white dresser.
Put the black rag on top of the small white dresser.
anns.task_desc: Move two rags from the tub to a small white dresser.

high_descs: Turn left and step forward to face the bath tub.
Pick up the dirty rag on the left side of the bath tub.
Turn right to face the table to the right of the sink.
Place the rag on the table to the right of the sink.
Turn left and step forward to face the bath tub.
Pick up the dirty rag on the right side of the bath tub.
Turn right to face the table to the right of the sink.
Place the rag on the table to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To move two dirty rags to the table to the right of the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the bath tub.
Grab the black cloth on the left.
Turn left and face the sink and dresser.
Place the cloth on the dresser.
Turn left back to the bath tub.
Grab the other cloth from the tub.
Head back to the sink.
Place the second cloth on the dresser as well.
anns.task_desc: Place two black cloths on the dresser.
